
purohith_id | Number (e.g., 1, 2, 3) | Auto-generated ID for each purohith. Like a roll number.
user_id | Number | Connects this profile to the main user account in your system.
approval_status | Text (e.g., PENDING, APPROVED) | Shows if the purohith is approved by admin or not.
experience_years | Number (e.g., 5, 10) | How many years of experience the purohith has.
specialization | Text | Which poojas / rituals he is expert in (e.g., weddings, griha pravesh).
languages_spoken | Text | Which languages he can speak (e.g., Telugu, Hindi, English).
bio | Text | A short introduction / about him.
address_line_1 | Text | House number, street etc.
address_line_2 | Text (optional) | Area / landmark (optional extra address info).
city | Text | City or town name.
state | Text | State name.
postal_code | Text (e.g., 500001) | PIN code.
aadhaar_card_no | Text | Aadhaar number of the purohith.
aadhaar_document_url | Text (link/path) | Link to uploaded Aadhaar file (photo/PDF) stored on server/cloud.
pancard_document_url | Text (link/path) | Link to PAN card or other ID proof file.
profile_photo_url | Text (link/path) | Link to the purohith‚Äôs profile photo.
other_documents_json | JSON (structured data) | Used to store multiple extra documents (certificates, proofs) with their type & link.
bank_name | Text | Purohith‚Äôs bank name.
account_number | Text | Purohith‚Äôs bank account number.
ifsc_code | Text | IFSC code of the bank branch.
created_at | Date & Time | When the profile was first created (system fills this automatically).
updated_at | Date & Time | When the profile was last updated (system fills/updates this automatically).

SQL QUERY üëç

CREATE TABLE purohith_profiles (
purohith_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
user_id INT NOT NULL REFERENCES users(user_id) ON DELETE CASCADE,
approval_status VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL DEFAULT 'PENDING',
experience_years INT,
specialization TEXT,
languages_spoken VARCHAR(255),
bio TEXT,
address_line_1 VARCHAR(255),
address_line_2 VARCHAR(255),
city VARCHAR(100),
state VARCHAR(100),
postal_code VARCHAR(20),
aadhaar_card_no VARCHAR(20),

-- Document upload fields (store only file links/paths)
aadhaar_document_url TEXT,
pancard_document_url TEXT,
profile_photo_url TEXT,
other_documents_json JSONB,

bank_name VARCHAR(100),
account_number VARCHAR(100),
ifsc_code VARCHAR(50),
created_at TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
updated_at TIMESTAMP WITH TIME ZONE NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
);

